and we got our shit off though,

37:17.135 --> 37:20.170
we did our shit proper though,
holla, holla, holla.

37:20.271 --> 37:23.442
I couldn't believe Julie,
Julie was like,

37:23.541 --> 37:25.911
"F every other cast,"
I'm like, "Really?"

