The fact that the trans
Black Lives Matter march

37:30.014 --> 37:32.284
went right by their flat,

37:33.117 --> 37:34.385
after all of the content

37:34.485 --> 37:36.355
that they were doing
in that direction,

37:36.454 --> 37:38.690
I was like, "How the hell
are we gonna come up

37:38.789 --> 37:41.192
