-That what?
-No.

38:05.617 --> 38:06.918
They didn't attack us by name.
I think, did he?

38:07.018 --> 38:09.054
Oh, no, this is not good.

38:09.153 --> 38:12.423
But at the same time,
I don't want to escalate things,

38:12.523 --> 38:14.793
