to forget it.

38:20.931 --> 38:22.601
A-And, my name is not Dave,
it's David.

38:22.701 --> 38:24.869
Well, you used to call Dom
Dominique all the time.

38:24.969 --> 38:26.804
I don't care, my name is David.

38:26.905 --> 38:29.440
If you want to be called David
just let us know, thank you.

38:29.541 --> 38:30.876
I'll call you David.

38:30.976 --> 38:33.244
[David] Thank you, king.

38:33.344 --> 38:35.045
-He's going there.
-What?

38:35.146 --> 38:36.181
-He's going there.
-Who's going there?

38:36.280 --> 38:38.784
-Dave... id.
-What?

38:38.884 --> 38:41.219
-David.
-Oh, oh, what's wrong?

38:41.318 --> 38:42.653
He threw a fucking apple at me.

38:42.753 --> 38:43.688
[Beth S] Wait a minute.

38:43.789 --> 38:45.123
[Glen] I ain't fucking doing it.

38:45.222 --> 38:47.324
I'm not doing it,
I'm not doing it.

38:48.226 --> 38:50.061
I'm just like,
"What the fuck, man?"

38:50.161 --> 38:51.295
[Jon] I'm worried about him,

38:51.396 --> 38:53.097
he's got some dependency
problems, y'all.

38:53.197 --> 38:55.266
David, he's hot and cold,

38:55.367 --> 38:58.804
and it's moments apart,
so it's not like a mood swing,

38:58.903 --> 39:02.139
but it's just...
He's unpredictable.

39:02.239 --> 39:03.509
Hey.

39:03.608 --> 39:05.043
That's why you've got
to follow your spirit.

39:05.143 --> 39:06.577
That's where you know
where people are at,

39:06.677 --> 39:08.780
you've got to follow that signal
that's in your heart.

39:08.880 --> 39:12.550
Spirit and soul, hey, family.
What you doing, bro?

39:22.360 --> 39:24.530
Y'all look like you was having
a meeting or something

39:24.630 --> 39:25.563
before I came up here.

39:25.664 --> 39:27.498
Dave, you know, if-if, um...

39:27.599 --> 39:30.601
-[David] My name is not Dave.
-Yeah, that's right, Dominique.

39:31.469 --> 39:34.873
[David] And it's really not,
legally or street-wise,

39:34.972 --> 39:36.206
my name is not Dave.

39:36.306 --> 39:37.307
[Glen] Dave, do you remember

39:37.409 --> 39:38.610
throwing something at me
tonight?

39:38.710 --> 39:41.813
Dave's a whole 'nother
motherfucker.

39:41.913 --> 39:43.213
[Jon]
I'm sitting there thinking,

39:43.313 --> 39:46.818
"Glen, hush, man.
Like, shut it for a minute."

39:46.918 --> 39:49.454
[Jon] David was extremely drunk.

39:49.554 --> 39:51.722
Now's a good time
to leave him alone.

39:51.822 --> 39:54.025
And, uh, I'm concerned for him.

39:55.460 --> 39:57.128
You know,
you're my replacement, right?

39:58.697 --> 40:01.800
[chuckles]

40:01.900 --> 40:03.601
What is happening right now?

40:03.702 --> 40:06.371
[David] No matter what,
you'll always be behind me.

40:06.472 --> 40:08.306
[laughs]

40:09.039 --> 40:11.342
Hey, hey, just...

40:12.077 --> 40:14.112
I know, hey.

40:20.719 --> 40:22.721
We're not gonna reason
with him right now.

40:23.889 --> 40:27.391
We were all getting along
really famously for two hours,

40:27.492 --> 40:29.427
and it was too good to be true.

40:29.527 --> 40:32.063
There may be a point of clarity
tomorrow,

40:32.163 --> 40:33.632
where we can say,
"Hey, dude, we're concerned."

40:35.666 --> 40:37.536
It's sad to see somebody
self de...

40:37.635 --> 40:39.137
[Beth S] What can we do
to help him?

40:39.237 --> 40:40.739
[Jon] Well, nothing
right at this moment.

40:40.838 --> 40:43.608
He's 50 years old, he's gonna
make his own decisions.

40:43.708 --> 40:47.344
But it's sad to watch
somebody self-destruct.

40:47.445 --> 40:49.280
I don't want to see him
self-destruct.

40:49.380 --> 40:51.583
So are we gonna turn this
into an intervention for David?

40:51.682 --> 40:53.918
Is this gonna become
an intervention?

40:54.385 --> 40:56.688
[Beth S] Would you feel okay
just, like, sitting back?

40:56.788 --> 40:58.789
It, like, it breaks my heart.

40:58.889 --> 41:01.159
He's... self-destructing.

41:07.398 --> 41:08.833
