41:08.934 --> 41:11.068
[Jon] He's self-destructing.

41:11.737 --> 41:16.007
I know that he has
the power within himself.

41:16.106 --> 41:17.976
We can't gang up
on him six on one.

41:18.076 --> 41:19.710
I would feel terrible about it.

41:19.811 --> 41:21.079
[Glen]
Maybe we should sleep on it,

41:21.179 --> 41:22.347
and maybe we'll come up
with something.

41:22.447 --> 41:24.382
Hey, Beth. You okay?

41:24.481 --> 41:26.885
No, did you see me get hit
tonight at the table?

41:26.985 --> 41:29.186
-He hit you?
-[Glen] Yeah!

41:29.286 --> 41:31.356
When I was joking
with Tami about the wigs,

41:31.456 --> 41:34.793
he got up and threw, like,
a pear or something at me.

41:35.460 --> 41:37.896
[Beth A] Glen is frustrated
with David,

41:37.996 --> 41:40.699
but I think that
he needs to just

41:40.798 --> 41:43.168
kind of chill out for a second.

41:43.268 --> 41:46.237
He has come off a hard ride,
and this is a lot,

41:46.336 --> 41:48.373
and it's a lot of emotion
in a short period of time.

41:48.472 --> 41:52.376
He's clearly been waiting
for 30 years for this moment,

41:52.476 --> 41:56.347
to be back in Tami's good
graces, it means a lot to him.

41:56.447 --> 42:00.184
Well, frankly,
the unpredictable behavior

42:00.284 --> 42:03.889
is what caused problems
back in the day.

42:04.655 --> 42:07.157
[sighs]

42:07.257 --> 42:11.028
[Jon] David's a mess, y'all.
David's volatile, he's a mess.

42:13.831 --> 42:15.833
[Glen] I mean,
what's gonna help him?

42:15.934 --> 42:18.536
We're with him
for the rest of this.

42:18.637 --> 42:20.806
[Jon] He's really drunk,

42:20.905 --> 42:23.608
so it's not an enjoyable David
that we're experiencing.

42:23.708 --> 42:27.478
And I'm having
a lot of concern about...

42:27.579 --> 42:30.547
substances that he's battling.

42:30.648 --> 42:32.083
He's gonna have to sleep
this off tonight.

42:32.182 --> 42:33.451
Why don't we make sure that

42:33.550 --> 42:35.452
we just don't have alcohol...

42:35.552 --> 42:36.788
-...available?
-In the house.

42:36.887 --> 42:38.056
-Yeah.
-[Glen] Yeah, I...

42:38.155 --> 42:39.625
Yeah, I would be willing
for that, too.

42:39.724 --> 42:42.327
-Let's box it up now.
-[Beth S] Okay.

42:43.494 --> 42:44.862
[Jon] This is a bad night,

42:44.963 --> 42:46.396
but I want David to be able
to redeem himself,

42:46.496 --> 42:49.034
and this was our chance
to support him.

42:49.134 --> 42:50.400
[Beth S] Let's just
get rid of it.

42:52.570 --> 42:53.838
[Jon] Here. That one, right?

42:54.739 --> 42:56.742
[Beth S] Oh, I don't...

42:56.842 --> 42:59.010
Oh, my God.

42:59.110 --> 43:01.045
Out back.

43:05.215 --> 43:07.351
[Beth S] Yeah.

