43:19.764 --> 43:22.099
[Beth A] Honey, I am home.

43:22.199 --> 43:24.302
-Ooh!
-[Beth S] This is beautiful!

43:24.402 --> 43:27.105
-[Jon] Oh, my.
-[Tami] Oh, now, this is nice.

43:27.204 --> 43:29.340
I can actually get through
this trip now.

43:29.440 --> 43:31.541
[Irene] I didn't want
another divorce,

43:31.643 --> 43:33.811
but I did it because I didn't
want my kids to grow up

43:33.911 --> 43:35.512
in a house with no love.

43:35.612 --> 43:37.447
[Jon] Irene,
I've never seen you happier

43:37.547 --> 43:39.184
than you have been with Phil.

43:39.284 --> 43:43.253
And the best part of it all
is that my kids love him.

43:43.353 --> 43:44.521
Well, this is very exciting.

43:44.621 --> 43:47.557
I love you with everything
I have.

43:48.525 --> 43:49.427
Aw.

43:49.527 --> 43:50.661
David, do you mind just not

43:50.762 --> 43:52.597
smoking weed at the table?

43:52.697 --> 43:54.666
I don't know
what her fucking problem is.

43:54.766 --> 43:56.934
What is it with her? What is it
with her that you're...

43:57.034 --> 43:58.635
I don't trust the bitch.

43:58.737 --> 44:00.838
-When I left my guard down.
-Let your guard down with what?

44:00.938 --> 44:03.141
-Against all the women...
-'Cause I asked you not to vape,

44:03.240 --> 44:04.409
and you blew smoke in my face.

44:04.509 --> 44:05.844
When you're willing
to let me talk

44:05.943 --> 44:07.778
and stop fucking cutting me off,
I shall return.

44:08.478 --> 44:10.014
When you go downstairs,

44:10.114 --> 44:13.117
pick up the eggshells that
you got everybody walking on.

